">报告和申诉流程</a>、 <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-community-guidelines-rewrite-170050737.html">重写社区政策</a>以及<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitch-takes-a-harder-stance-against-explicit-deepfakes-175407437.html">对深度造假采取更强硬的立场</a>。 “我们知道，人们希望我们在这个领域做得更多，而我们只是一次解决了一部分问题，”费舍尔说。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/twitch-streamers-can-soon-block-banned-accounts-from-tuning-in-195923803.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/twitch-streamers-can-soon-block-banned-accounts-from-tuning-in-195923803.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8cf878fe-68a1-479d-92e9-f9a63bee0b19</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 18 Aug 2023 19:59:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692388765</ingested><modified> 2023-08-18T19:59:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1224" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/79b3e960-3e00-11ee-bbfc-f137893cc1ef" width="2179"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1224" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/79b3e960-3e00-11ee-bbfc-f137893cc1ef" width="2179"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:descrip